headline: Magda Gegenava, chef: 'I became familiar with street food and adapted my recipes so they could be eaten on the go'
description: 'Refuge Recipes' (3/6). This summer, chefs from Refugee Food, a group celebrating its 10th anniversary, are sharing the dish that best defines them.
